doctype html
html
  body
    p Hi #{first_name} #{last_name},
    if test
      h4 This is a test email. Please ignore it.
    p This is an automated email from WMCN. 
    p If you are receiving this email it means your show has been accepted for the upcoming semester! 
      span Expect an email from WMCN staff shortly with schedule information.
      
    p Here is your login information for WMCN.fm, where you will create your playlists every week:
    p Email: #{email}
    p Password: #{password}
    p This is a temporary auto-generated password, that you can reset at 
      a(href='http://wmcn.fm/admin/user') the user page
      span once you've logged in with the above information.
    p If you have any questions or problems with the website, please contact the 
      span web director listed on the 
      a(href='http://wmcn.fm/staff') staff page.
    p Peace, love, and happy DJing,
    p WMCN staff
